i drive a autostruted kal powered ion ssto(this thing works normally only in low atmosphere and obliterates its enviorment while protecting itsself(service bay+heat shield) against the winds(still not recommended to full throttle on high atmosphere,as long as its not having twr<1 problems)) with bill bob and val and a 3d printer and an advanced isru set (for ore centrefuging not fuel if we get on a planet) and capture jeb and get an escape route of kerbol while still accelerating at 100m/s^2 (yes,10g,almost the maximum to avoid problems like kerbals sleeping or things destroying)  but not knowing where to go

current speed shown on navball(to default,orbit,ref kerbol):30000m/s

They clean it up a wear space suits until it is
CCC Forces arrive to assist with the cleanup and succeeded in prevented any further leakage.

We build a web of Ground-Air missile silos all around the KSC
